data.description: This move in ready home is a must see! Located in Churchill Subdivision this 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath property has a very open easy-living floor plan. The inside trim and walls have been freshly painted, the carpets professionally cleaned, the house has been washed, and the landscaping has been spruced up for the new owner! The kitchen has an island bar with granite counter tops, refrigerator, electric oven and cook top, and all of the appliances are stainless steel. The primary bedroom includes a double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, and a walk in closet as well. The Living room is spacious with an open floor plan, vaulted ceiling, and opens to the kitchen with matching wood styled vinyl flooring. The neighborhood has great amenities with an outdoor pool, BBQ area, and playground. This home is also gold fortified so enjoy those lower insurance rates and a safe home! Come check it out!
